  "short_description": "Kirakira slimes are adorable, chubby and defenseless creatures. They're vulnerable to most of the world's perils by themselves, but together they’re unbeatable. Fuse, combine and power up your slimes in this indie puzzle game, either by playing in local versus or all by yourself!",
