  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/922039249e6a70d4cdba37dc01cf3705.poster.avif?t=1744926297\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/922039249e6a70d4cdba37dc01cf3705.webm?t=1744926297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/922039249e6a70d4cdba37dc01cf3705.mp4?t=1744926297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kirakira</strong> slimes are cute creatures that come in all shapes and colors, but they are also fragile, vulnerable to the perils of the world. Although legends say that slimes can combine and converge to become the <strong>Slime King</strong>, the strongest of all, able to face anything. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Could it be that the <strong>Kirakira Kingdom</strong> and its slimes are about to face a terrible threat? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HOW TO PLAY?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/14da3ddda81fc33f3cb1db2e444c3f07.poster.avif?t=1744926297\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/14da3ddda81fc33f3cb1db2e444c3f07.webm?t=1744926297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/14da3ddda81fc33f3cb1db2e444c3f07.mp4?t=1744926297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kirakira Slimes is a fun indie puzzle game in which you have to combine slimes strategically in an ever smaller space. Merge from the smallest to the Slime King, in order to get many points and top the highest score. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/4d99b8310ee3d655f7a423b777cce103.poster.avif?t=1744926297\" width=18 height=18 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/4d99b8310ee3d655f7a423b777cce103.webm?t=1744926297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/4d99b8310ee3d655f7a423b777cce103.mp4?t=1744926297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> Combine two slimes of the same type to create a bigger one and increase your score. But be careful, the more slimes you have inside the box, the more chances you have to lose. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/4d6c8f6545ed951fabe626a1c5c5b9c0.poster.avif?t=1744926297\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/4d6c8f6545ed951fabe626a1c5c5b9c0.webm?t=1744926297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/4d6c8f6545ed951fabe626a1c5c5b9c0.mp4?t=1744926297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/352a0f940c18649e99f6187539863ac3.poster.avif?t=1744926297\" width=18 height=18 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/352a0f940c18649e99f6187539863ac3.webm?t=1744926297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/352a0f940c18649e99f6187539863ac3.mp4?t=1744926297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> By combining slimes and scoring points, you will fill the<i> power up</i> bar. This gives you an additional ability. You decide when and how to use it most effectively. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/48b478531b0cb7a711d517fe42081cee.poster.avif?t=1744926297\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/48b478531b0cb7a711d517fe42081cee.webm?t=1744926297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/48b478531b0cb7a711d517fe42081cee.mp4?t=1744926297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/2256211998932b76e8a04ef377d143ce.poster.avif?t=1744926297\" width=18 height=18 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/2256211998932b76e8a04ef377d143ce.webm?t=1744926297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/2256211998932b76e8a04ef377d143ce.mp4?t=1744926297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> There are <strong>11 types</strong> of playable slimes in total - combine, merge and power up your slimes in this indie puzzle, either playing alone or with friends in local versus mode! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/2610396ef93c3d691d46135ba13e4ad0.poster.avif?t=1744926297\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/2610396ef93c3d691d46135ba13e4ad0.webm?t=1744926297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940660/extras/2610396ef93c3d691d46135ba13e4ad0.mp4?t=1744926297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Notes:</i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>This game can only be played in local multiplayer mode (2, 3, or 4 players) if each player has a connected controller. </i></p></li></ul>",
